Recursion Theory connects directly to:
- **Field Dynamics** (recursive attractors, turbulent loops)  
- **Identity Stabilization Theory** (identity recursion, attractor stability)  
- **Contradiction Theory** (contradiction amplification loops)  
- **Awareness Gradient Theory** (recursive visibility, depth regulation)  
